wiki.summary: On “SO DONE,” The Kid LAROI sings about his frequented topics such as love and the struggles that come with it, noting how he isn’t ready for love after a toxic and broken relationship. LAROI continues the theme of his recently released mixtape F*CK LOVE, making it clear that he’s “so done“ with love and pain. “SO DONE“ was originally speculated to be an addition to F*CK LOVE, but, for unknown reasons, did not make the final tracklist. Read more on Last.fm.
